          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-4200 tests: Add debugging for replace_nids errors",
        "message": "LU-4200 tests: Add debugging for replace_nids errors\n\nDuring conf-sanity/66 lctl replace_nids returns \"Operation now in\nprogress\" which comes from an error in mgs_llog.c::mgs_replace_nids()\nfailing the only_mgs_is_running test.\n\nThis code will print the paramters that only_mgs_is_running() makes\nit's determination on, to hopefully determine why it's failing.\n\nSigned-off-by: Nathaniel Clark <nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I523704b6fda3d600347c27d78d39bdd887602e28\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
